<title>UK: CLF Hypo sets 100 mln mark step-up Dec 2001 bond.</title>
<headline>CLF Hypo sets 100 mln mark step-up Dec 2001 bond.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following bond was announced by lead manager Morgan Stanley.</p>
<p> BORROWER   CLF HPOTHEKENBANK BERLIN AG</p>
<p> AMT    100 MLN DEM   COUPON    *4.0	 MATURITY   *10.DEC.01</p>
<p> TYPE	 STEP-UP   ISS PRICE  101.90    PAY DATE  S-10.JUN.97</p>
<p> FULL FEES  2.00	REOFFER    PAR (REC) SPREAD	 =</p>
<p> MOODY	=	   LISTING    BERLIN    PAY FREQ    =</p>
<p> S&amp;P	  =	   DENOMS (K) 10	  SALE LIMITS =</p>
<p> NEG PLG    NO	  CRS DEFLT  NO	  FORCE MAJ   YES</p>
<p> GOV LAW    GERMAN    HOME CTRY  GERMANY   TAX PROVS   STANDARD</p>
<p> MGT/UND    0.10	SELL CONC  1.90	PRAECIPUUM  =</p>
<p> NOTES     *TO 10.DEC.97 THEN STEPS-UP TO 4.875 PCT THEREAFTER</p>
<p>		IF NOT CALLED AT PAR.</p>
<p>		S-SHORT FIRST COUPON</p>
